Class ServicesManagement

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management.AConnectionManager
      • cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management.ServicesManagement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISSConnectionManager, java.lang.Runnable
    public class ServicesManagement
extends AConnectionManager
implements java.lang.Runnable, ISSConnectionManager

    The class of ServicesManagement is used to abstractly define the type of the instances.

    This instance is used as a container of connections with services from router.

    Written for project "Connections2".

    03. 04. 2020 .vse.java.connections.routerSide
